{## SelectPlus Virtual Field Definitions
{---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------}
    Each block below defines a virtual field for the SelectPlus plugin to render & save.

    Virtual Fields can be defined directly in a SelectPlus `.json` config ...

    BUT ..

    Since all files in this folder get parsed by twig (regardless of file extension),
    this file is a handy way to avoid needless duplication of commonly used fields.

    And also lets us provide a little documentation for each field.

    Usage example:

        "virtuals" : [
            {{ block( 'spacer', '_config/_virtuals' ) }},
            {{ block( 'limit',  '_config/_virtuals' ) }}
        ],

    Caveats:

        1) Do not use this file as a SelectPlus config file. It will not work.
        2) Mind your JSON syntax. Twig will not catch errors in this file or
           when including Twig syntax in JSON files.

 -> https://github.com/simplicateca/craft-selectplus-field/blob/main/README.md
{-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##}

